<center><h3>Departments</h3></center>


<hr>



<table border=0 cellpadding="10"><tr valign="top">
<td><b><a href="/heritage/p_review/sept96/wepeo.html">We the People</a></b><br>
<I>Adam Meyerson on a rating system for social-service agencies</I></td>
