http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/heritage/library/categories/education/lect564.html 204.71.237.92 19970115122941 text/html 35106
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 15-Jan-97 12:29:40 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 10-Jan-97 19:33:44 GMT
