<li><I> Ibid.</i><p>
<li>    CBO, <I>Auctioning Radio Spectrum Licenses</I>, March 1992, p. 3.<p>
<li>    Progress and Freedom Foundation, <I>The Telecom Revolution: An American Opportunity</I>, May 1995, p. 17.<p>
